ggplot2 Cheat Sheet:
Two Variables: Continuous Bivariate Distribution

library(ggplot2)

Bins in 2D

p <- ggplot(diamonds, aes(carat, price))
p <- p + geom_bin2d(binwidth = c(0.25, 500))
print(p)

Density in 2D

p <- ggplot(diamonds, aes(carat, price))
p <- p + geom_density2d()
print(p)

Hexagons

p <- ggplot(diamonds, aes(carat, price))
p <- p + geom_hex()
print(p)
